p: \bNasca Town is known throughout the Torren Region for its fabulous Safari Zone.
\bWe're not talking about no Friend Safari rubbish either- this is the real deal!
\bOn one hand, I'm so glad we have people like the Augur to protect us.
\bBut on the other... well, he's so good at his job, we don't need a police force!
\bI've been laid off, which really sucks.
\bAfter the scandals with the Second Augur and Zachary it became clear we should be making more of an effort to investigate what people in power are doing
behind the scenes. \nPersonally, I'm just glad to have my job back!
\rThese farms have been here for as long as I can remember.
\rI hope one day I'll be able to tend to them, like my mother before me. And her mother before her!
\rThe northern part of Torren has way less people than places like Helios.
\rIt's a shame really, it's a lot harder to make friends.
\bI used to scour routes when I looked for Pokemon, but I don't really do that anymore.
\bI find all that I need in the Safari Zone now!
\bThat does make all these extra Repels a bit useless, though.
\bI used to scour routes when I looked for Pokemon, but I don't really do that anymore.
\rI heard they were going to do a bust on the Black Market under Helios.
\rUh, I mean... great! Shut it down!
\rPraise the Augur! Everything he does is wonderful!
\rI heard they were going to do a bust on the Black Market under Helios.
\rIt's nice that I can actually talk about this now that the Augur's stepped down.
\bThe Torren Region is so much more beautiful than my homeland.
\bThough, in fairness, Vesryn isn't really in a very good state right now.
\bMy Donphan help guard the plants from pesky Pokemon.
\bPokemon like Yanmega and Bunnelby are always trying to munch on our hard work!
\bWe here in Nasca grow food and crops for all over the region!
\bBetween all of our farmland and our Safari Zone, our town makes a fair amount per year!
\rI market my Milk for weary travellers!
